<abstract>

<para>This document is intended to help you to get PPR up and running as
quicly as possible.  It does not attempt to describe all of PPR's features
or theory of operation.  More information can be found in <ulink
url="../pprdoc/pprdoc.html"><citetitle>PPR, a Print Spooler for
PostScript</citetitle></ulink>, the <ulink url="../refman/"><citetitle>PPR
Reference Manual</citetitle></ulink>, and the <ulink
url="../pprhack/pprhack.html"><citetitle>PPR Hackers
Guide</citetitle></ulink>.</para>

</abstract>

