<sect1 id="adding">
<title>Adding Printers</title>

<para>This section has several parts. This is because adding printers
may be a multi-step process. For example, you might add a printer
to <application>PPR</application>, them make it a member of a
<application>PPR</application> group, then tell
<application>Samba</application> about it, then add it to the printers
shared by PPR's AppleTalk print server.</para>

